data.name: ProcedureResult
desc: determines whether a procedure returns a result or not.

items.name: UNKNOWN
lines: A possible value for column PROCEDURE_TYPE in the com.sun.star.sdbc.XResultSet object returned by the method com.sun.star.sdbc.XDatabaseMetaData.getProcedures().
Indicates that it is not known whether the procedure returns a result.

items.name: NONE
lines: A possible value for column PROCEDURE_TYPE in the com.sun.star.sdbc.XResultSet object returned by the method com.sun.star.sdbc.XDatabaseMetaData.getProcedures().
Indicates that the procedure does not return a result.

items.name: RETURN
lines: A possible value for column PROCEDURE_TYPE in the com.sun.star.sdbc.XResultSet object returned by the method com.sun.star.sdbc.XDatabaseMetaData.getProcedures().
Indicates that the procedure returns a result.
